name: Amour Preuve Hoodie
description:
This item is part of the all new exclusive French collection, Amour Preuve by Love Proof.

Super soft and cuddly hoodie with double-bevelled edge at its hood along with a cord in the same colour. It offers a kangaroo pocket outside and very soft fleece inside to provide best comfort wear. The hoodie is cut straight and is slightly fit to the body. It features pronounced sleeve cuffs as well as a prominent waistband hem and kangaroo pocket fringes. Thanks to its high 320 g/m² consistency and its polyester fraction it will always fit after washing. 80% cotton, 20% polyester.

Model: Jozey - Wearing a size small.

name: Amour Preuve Beanie
description:
This item is part of the all new exclusive French collection, Amour Preuve by Love Proof.

This practical beanie does exactly what you think it will – keep your head warm when it’s getting colder out there. And your ears will thank you for wearing it as well. The hat is easy to wear and just as easy to stow away in your pocket or bag. One size fits all. 100% acrylic.

name: Amour Preuve White Sweatshirt
description:
This item is part of the all new exclusive French collection, Amour Preuve by Love Proof.

The fleecy inner lining makes this sweatshirt cosy, warm and comfortable to wear. The fabric has a high cotton percentage at 80% and weighs a heavy 320g/m². Double-stitched sleeves and collar make this a durable and long-lasting sweatshirt.

name: Love Proof Cuffed Dress [PRE-ORDER]
description:
Release date for this item has not been set yet.

All pre-orders will be delivered on the release date or in some cases, a day before the official release date.

Love Proof presents the first part of the all new women's wear starting with the cuffed dress. This is the ideal dress for the ladies on a night out. It consists of a simple design but one that will easily catch the eye of others. The polyester and elastane dress material is joined by leather panels located on the end of the arm.

name: Love Proof Shisha Pen
Love Proof Women's Red & White College Jacket
description: Gear up American college-style. This cult jacket made of cotton will get you extra points on campus and beyond. Buttons, pockets, contrasting stripes and rib cuffs combine for a collegiate look to create this special style. And, to be fair: nobody needs to know that we’ve never seen an American university from inside. Consistency: 380 g/m², 65% cotton, 35% polyester.

name: Love Proof Ace of Spades Black & White T-Shirt
description: This classic t-shirt offers a straight and slightly form-fitting cut. A sewn-in neckband provides for comfort wear. The ring-spun cotton fabrics of this high-quality t-shirt make sure that it is soft to the touch and that it will keep its shape after many washings (fabric weight: 146g/m²). Made by US fashion brand American Apparel from Los Angeles, CA! 100% cotton (except for colour code heather grey: 90% cotton, 10% polyester).

name: Love Proof Ace of Spades iPhone 4/4S/5 Case
description: Your iPhone will to suit you to a T when this snap-on case shows your message or design on its backside. Of course all ports and connections as well as the camera are readily accessible, while the side material boasts a low-keyed black. You will appreciate this elegant and pleasantly light accessory to get your style across. Made from metal and plastic.

name: Love Proof Backpack & Beanie Hat
description:
